name: 90 Football
blurb: 90 is a football game blending street games, professional leagues and off the pitch antics into one complete game.

rewards.reward: The Game - Make 90 happen with a Huge Thanks, Website Credit & Email Updates:\r\nFor a pledge of \u00a31 you will gain our gratitude and thanks from everyone at Frenetic for helping to make 90 happen. We will also give you regular email updates on the progress of 90 and a backer credit on our website. And a copy of the game for iOS and/or Android when available.

In-Game Credits, Forum Badge &  a Huge Thanks with Email Updates:\r\nWith a pledge of \u00a32 you will receive the \u00a31 rewards as well as a receiving a mention within our in-game credits for making 90 possible. We will also give you an exclusive forum badge to identify you as one of our backers.

Exclusive Atom Kit: Compression Armour + Shin Guards + Boots = Kickstarter Collection Bonus:\r\nFor \u00a35 you will receive the previous pledge + Kickstarter Collection Bonus which includes an exclusive kit including Compression Armour, Shin Guards and Boots. Each of the items will include a stat bonus for your character in-game with a complete kit stat bonus applied when using all 3 items together.

90 in-game Pinball Machine. Playable Arcade Cabinet + Kickstarter Atom Kit with Collection Bonus: A pledge of \u00a315 will give you all the above along with the pinball machine and the playable arcade cabinet. The arcade machine has its own high score leaderboard.

Exclusive room + 90 in-game Pinball Machine + Kickstarter Collection Bonus: \r\nA pledge of \u00a325 will give the previous pledge + you get a cool exclusive pinball machine for your (in-game) apartment and the playable arcade cabinet. Also an exclusive hidden room available within your apartment. The exclusive room will add an additional feature to your apartment, 3 secret rooms are available for you to choose from. This room will not be available in the main game and is only unlocked for our Kickstarter backers.

Exclusive Room + 90 in-game Pinball Machine + Playable Arcade Game + Kickstarter Bonus + Golden Phoenix  Boots: For a \u00a350 pledge the rewards will include all the previous pledges + the Golden Phoenix Boots. These Boots offer a huge stat boost for your player affecting the physical stats of your character.  Phoenix Boots available to Kickstarter backers only!

Graffiti your name into the Street Pitch: We will turn your name (or a name of your choice) into graffiti around the street pitch. Where it will remain for all to see! + Exclusive hidden room + Golden Phoenix Boots and previous pledges (Limit to 20)

Become an in-game character: The \u00a3500 pledge  will allow you to have your appearance placed within 90 as a non-playable character (NPC). The character will be in a prime area of the game where you will be seen frequently by everyone playing the game. + Pledges 1-6 including the Exclusive hidden room + Golden Phoenix Boots and a dedicated in-game character credit so everyone knows its you!

In-Game Advertising on the Newspaper: For a pledge of \u00a31000 we will offer a chance to feature as one of our in-game advertisers seen by everyone that plays 90. At this level, your advertisement will have a prominent place on our in-game newspaper which appears after each match and at key events during the game. (please note; with this pledge some conditions apply please see 90football.com for more details)

In-Game Advertising on the Pitch: Our highest pledge of \u00a32500 is the chance to be one of our football pitch advertisers. Similar to professional football with advertising boards, we will feature your advert on the side of our pitch, which will be seen by our players on match days. (please note; with this pledge some conditions apply please see 90football.com for more details)
